(3, 'Dell Pro 15 Essentials PV15250 Intel® Core™ i5 1334U', 'Dell', 'Servers & Data Center', 'DELL Pro 15 essential PV15250 13th Generation | Intel® Core™ i5 1334U Processor | 8GB DDR5 Ram | 512GB SSD | 15.6″ FHD (1920 x 1080) Anti-glare Display | Intel® UHD Graphics | Carbon Black | New', 12120, 1, 'https://laptophouse.pk/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/aa-4012-2471496-181025120216500.webp'),
(4, 'Sony 1000X THE COLLEXION Premium Wireless Noise Canceling Headphones | WH-1000XX', 'Sony', 'Workstations & Laptops', '1000X series 10th anniversary edition.\nLuxury design, calibrated for comfort: Curated materials meet meticulous craftmanship, appealing to both sight and touch. Premium crafted metal and refined faux leather deliver understand elegance.\nSound to transport you: Rich, wide-range sound elevates every listening experience. A bespoke driver, paired with co-creation with renowned mastering engineers, delivers balanced lows, natural vocals and clear highs with effortless clarity. 360 Upmix further expands music, cinema and gaming contents into an immersive special soundscape.\nPower behind performance: The HD Noise Cancelling Processor QN3 advances D/A conversion, while the Integrated Processor V3 allows 360 Upmix to support three modes and DSEE Ultimate.\nLegendary 1000X series noise cancelling: Quiet, down to the finest detail. Powered by advanced processors and an adaptive microphone system, noise cancelling is optimized in real time-so your world stays undistributed, and your sound stays pure.\nUltra-clear calls: Clarity in every call, AI beamforming and V3 processor isolate your voice from background noise, so you\'re always heard-even when others are talking, \nEffortlessly intuitive: Thoughtful design means true integration. Touch controls for complete playback and volume, plus smart features like voice assistance and automatic wearing and speech detection making listening seamless. \nMusic as the artist intended: Through collaboration with top mastering engineers, 1000X THE COLLEXION reproduces music with smooth vocals, clear instrument balance, and nuanced dynamics, faithfully conveying the creators intent.', 2499, 1, 'https://sonyworld.ae/cdn/shop/files/01-1000X_THE_COLLEXION.jpg?v=1779183916&width=533'),
